- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes a learning framework for bias estimation. 
- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) is relevant as recommendation systems often rely on social network information. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is relevant as the paper proposes an optimization framework for bias learning. 
- cs.DB (Databases) is relevant as recommendation systems often rely on large databases of user-item interactions.
